(以下简称《暂行办法》) 的通知。 《暂行办法》规定，资金账户可以由参加人在开办个人养老金业务的商业银行开立或指定，也可以由参加人通过其他符合规定的个人养老金产品销售机构，在开办个人养老金业务的商业银行指定，但不得由个人养老金产品销售机构直接在商业银行开立。 《暂行办法》明确，商业银行发行与代销的个人养老金产品，应当符合金融监管机构有关规定。商业银行不得向参加人推荐和销售不符合金融监管机构规定的个人养老金产品。 《暂行办法》要求，个人养老金理财产品发行机构和销售机构应当按照法律法规及相关监管规定，通过公开渠道，真实准确、合理客观、简明扼要地披露个人养老金理财产品相关信息，不得宣传策略保本，不得承诺或宣传保本保收益。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-07efa79b65b1681c015f57c125eeeeb4_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/567450168"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IupyFzoCGlucfEAMaCDg4MzgyNTMzINHK3ZsGMAM4owFAFHIJNTY3NDUwMTY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1668812659.9736438", "card_id": "Q_543662848", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Intel 和 AMD 有没有重新考虑做 ARM 处理器？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "毕竟苹果笔记本都用的 ARM 架构 M2，市场还是很大的。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/543662848"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IupyFzoCGlucfEAMaCDgzMDk2NTM2IMroypYGMAM4VUAVcgk1NDM2NjI4NDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1668812659.974171", "card_id": "Q_565762821", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "钱对生活有什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/565762821"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IupyFzoCGlucfEAMaCDg4MDA3MDg2IN6VsZsGMAE4lQFAFnIJNTY1NzYyODIxeACqA